Quickstrike:




Quickstrike immediately made his way to the command room. He had been 
following Inferno from a distance, being weary of Inferno. He didn't 
understand when he said Royalty. 

He looked around the area. "Sugar-bot, ya want me t' go now?" he 
asked.
